data.description:
A 1965 one-story Rambler on a quiet cul-de-sac in the city limits of Liberty Hill, Texas. 5 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, 2 living, 2 dinings, 3540 sq ft. New tornado-proof roof with transferable warranty, new paint outside.  Backs to a Church and on a street that is building new $500K houses on 1/4 acre lots or less. The same family has lived and raised children here for 22 years. Liberty Hill is one of the fastest growing cities in Texas, and an opportunity for you to get in on the ground floor of a rapidly developing town. An investor's paradise awaits the buyer of this property as land value skyrocket. 

\
